    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute beauty! It is in truly pristine condition and has been pampered since day one\u2014honestly, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s a total dream to drive, spotless inside and out, and I\u2019ve made sure everything is perfect for the next owner. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, you\u2019ve found it! Drop me a message, I\u2019d love to chat and get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
