    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the marque's engineering pinnacle. Power is delivered via the legendary S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains factory-spec with zero structural fatigue, benefiting from a documented subframe reinforcement and a meticulously maintained suspension setup featuring MacPherson struts and a multi-link rear end. Shifting is handled by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, sending torque through a variable M differential lock. Every mechanical component, from the cross-drilled rotors to the bushings, exhibits zero play, ensuring original-factory turn-in and lateral grip. This is a concours-level driver\u2019s car for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
