    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the definition of showroom ready. Finished in a deep, ceramic-coated metallic paint that looks as wet as the day it rolled off the assembly line, there isn't a single swirl mark, door ding, or stone chip to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in an untouched state; the premium leather seats still retain their factory-fresh scent and firm bolstering, with zero signs of creasing or wear. Every electronic feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the high-fidelity surround sound system, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a meticulous service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule at certified dealerships. The engine bay is immaculate, reflecting the same level of care as the pristine undercarriage. It sits on flawless alloy wheels wrapped in brand-new, high-performance tires. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment and treated with absolute reverence. It is, quite simply, as close to a new car as a pre-owned vehicle can get.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
